messages.message: Can someone help me out with more credits please? I have a demo in 2 hours

Also: I got unlucky in that my previous TPAM access request _just_ expired this morning.
ah ok, i'll follow up with @shaunak on this; ideally we have a process and the right people are enabled to give credits, and they don't have to be in Eng hopefully
OK, looks like I finally got access just now. @Mark it's probably too late, but you should have the credits now.
@mfichman can we install a license in such a way that everyone with .instabase.com (http://instabase.com) domain has infinite credits for AIHub Product?

Unfortunately, no -- license-service isn't able to match the email suffix of a user in that way. I could possibly manually add all instabase.com (http://instabase.com) users to the license via license assignments, but I haven't tested that configuration with AI Hub.
